'''頭髮胸罩'''（{{lang-en|Hair bra}}），是指女性用自己的[[頭髮|頭髮]]遮住[[乳頭|乳頭]]及[[乳暈|乳暈]]的[[攝影|攝影]]姿勢<ref name="dym">{{Cite news|title=Janice Turner: Is the misogyny of lads' mags good clean fun?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/2005/oct/22/weekend7.weekend3|newspaper=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2005-10-21|accessdate=2020-10-16|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Janice|last=Turner|quote=The cover model's breast is partially concealed by her cupped hand. 'We call that shot "hand-bra",' says Paul Merrill, launch editor of ''Zoo'' and now in charge of international editions, 'We use that a lot.' He flicks to a cover showing a model whose hair extensions cover her nipples: 'This is hair-bra,' he says.|archive-date=2019-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830112918/https://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/2005/oct/22/weekend7.weekend3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若是頭髮長度未到達乳頭，用假髮代替頭髮遮住乳頭也算是頭髮胸罩。一般是已進入[[青春期|青春期]]的女性才會需要以此姿勢避免暴露乳頭。

頭髮胸罩和用手遮住乳頭及乳暈的[[手胸罩|手胸罩]]一樣都屬於[[半裸體|半裸體]]，有很強的煽情效果。如果是在像一些[[漫畫|漫畫]]或[[動畫|動畫]]中，女性限制不能露出乳頭及乳暈，需用頭髮胸罩的方式避免，可能會在該角色中設定為[[長髮|長髮]]。

像[[濱崎步|濱崎步]]在其專輯《[[Appears|Appears]]》封面的造型，就是頭髮胸罩的半裸體照片，而台灣藝人[[李愛綺|李愛綺]]（李嘉）2010年專輯的宣傳照也有頭髮胸罩的照片<ref>{{cite web|title=有圖／長髮遮兩點 李嘉全裸挑戰台語歌壇|url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2010/12/02/584262|accessdate=2014-06-26|publisher=Nownews.com|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531124700/http://www.nownews.com/n/2010/12/02/584262|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

